WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
Welcome to the RestoreAssist Setup Wizard.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
This is the 5-step process that activates your workspace.

00:16.000 --> 00:21.906
Step 1: Business Profile.

00:21.906 --> 00:29.906
Confirm your business name, ABN, and upload your logo.

00:29.906 --> 00:34.866
Step 2: AI Hydration.

00:34.866 --> 00:42.866
Industry defaults are auto-loaded — S500 standards, WHS checklists, report templates, and insurer profiles.

00:42.866 --> 00:47.827
Step 3: Integrations.

00:47.827 --> 00:55.827
Connect Xero, MYOB, QuickBooks, and job management tools.

00:55.827 --> 01:00.787
Step 4: Health Check.

01:00.787 --> 01:06.220
Verify 12 capabilities.

01:06.220 --> 01:10.236
Step 5: Activate.

01:10.236 --> 01:18.236
One tap and your workspace is live.

01:18.236 --> 01:24.850
Your dashboard is now ready.